<title>Gec Limitations</title>

<para>
The following Eiffel constructs have not been implemented yet:

<blockquote>
<variablelist>
	<varlistentry>
		<term>Storable</term>
		<listitem><para>
			does not support classes `MISMATCH_CORRECTOR`, `CLASS_NAME_TRANSLATIONS`,
			nor the note tag "storable_version" yet
		</para></listitem>
	</varlistentry>
	<varlistentry>
		<term>Non-conforming inheritance</term>
		<listitem><para>
			feature replication still uses the pre-ECMA semantics of 'select'
		</para></listitem>
	</varlistentry>
	<varlistentry>
		<term>Debugger</term>
		<listitem></listitem>
	</varlistentry>
	<varlistentry>
		<term>Profiler</term>
		<listitem></listitem>
	</varlistentry>
	<varlistentry>
		<term>Cecil (C to Eiffel interface)</term>
		<listitem></listitem>
	</varlistentry>
	<varlistentry>
		<term>Eiffel for .Net</term>
		<listitem></listitem>
	</varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</blockquote>

Note that this list is not exhaustive.
</para>

